{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC02_REG_160.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x26,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Mix Master, can I get a crawfish pizza, a cherry parfait, and some water?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x141,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "W-Water!? You're so simple, Ayesha.<CR>It's rare for someone to order water<CR>at a tavern."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x143,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "As the Mix Master, drink orders are where I really get to show off my skills."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...but water goes best with the cherry parfait."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Well, if you feel that strongly about it, I guess I have no choice. All right, one water coming up!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "And, what would you like?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I'll...hmm... I guess I'll start with the hard liquor! Give me one that's got a high proof!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Oh, wow. Are you sure you should order hard liquor during the day?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Don't worry, I've done it plenty of times before! I want a delicious one please!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x110,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "A delicious one... To be frank and earnest, I can't drink, so I'm not really sure what to give you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x112,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "But all of my alcohol has been<CR>recommended by the supplier,<CR>so I can guarantee the taste."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "What a waste... I feel bad for you,<CR>not being able to drink something<CR>so delicious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa7,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. I've tried to train myself,<CR>but I guess my genealogy just won't<CR>allow it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa9,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "My mom, dad, grandma and grandpa...my whole family can't drink alcohol."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xaa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Because of that, even at big ceremonies, like weddings, my family is always sober."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "(Alcohol... I get drunk from just the smell, too...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I see. Now that I think about it, my mom and dad are bottomless..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I guess that's why I have a high tolerance. Yeah, I have to thank my parents next time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Being bottomless is kinda scary, too. Alcohol is best enjoyed in moderation."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "But if we were to have kids,<CR>they might be moderate."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "So...whattaya think about me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Uhhh..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What's with that expression?<CR>I'm slightly hurt..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "But still, you? I don't really care if a guy's older or younger than me, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "A guy that's shorter than me is a deal breaker. If I'm going out, I want my guy to be tall."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Huh? But I'm taller than you, aren't I?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Ehh, really? I think we're about the same, or you might be slightly shorter."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "That's because of the height of your heels. My shoes are flat."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "I can't stand guys who are this picky. Guys need to have a big heart."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Ugh... Hey, Ayesha, say something to her."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Like how the value of a guy isn't based on their height, or how I'm actually taller than her..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Umm...well, everyone has their own values."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Oh, but I've also heard that someone's height can differ depending on the time of day."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "I heard that you're tallest in the morning! So if you compare heights in the morning... Huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x110,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "It's obvious that you're using your words carefully..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x111,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, your intended kindness is piercing my heart instead."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, Ayesha, you're sinful as well. Anyways...Mix Master, I want seconds!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x112,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "Okay, okay... Coming right up."
        }
    ]
}